          <div id="ysms-back-in-stock-error-message" class="ysms-back-in-stock-error-message" style="display: none;">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 512 512" fill="currentColor">
              <<path d="M27.4 432L0 480l55.3 0 401.4 0 55.3 0-27.4-48L283.6 80.4 256 32 228.4 80.4 27.4 432zm401.9 0L82.7 432 256 128.7 429.3 432zM232 296l0 24 48 0 0-24 0-88-48 0 0 88zm48 104l0-48-48 0 0 48 48 0z"/>
            </svg>
            <p>Hay un error con tu número de teléfono</p>
          </div>

          
            <button
              form="ysms-back-in-stock-form"
              type="submit"
              id="ysms-back-in-stock-submit"
              class="ysms-back-in-stock-submit"
            >
              Notificarme cuando esté disponible
            </button>
          

          <div
            id="ysms-back-in-stock-success-message"
            class="ysms-back-in-stock-success-message"
            style="display: none;"
          >
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 512 512" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M256 512A256 256 0 1 0 256 0a256 256 0 1 0 0 512zM369 209L241 337l-17 17-17-17-64-64-17-17L160 222.1l17 17 47 47L335 175l17-17L385.9 192l-17 17z"/>
            </svg>
            <p>Te notificaremos tan pronto como el producto esté disponible nuevamente.</p>
          </div>
        </form>
      </main><footer>
          <a
            href="https://apps.shopify.com/ysms?utm_source=back_in_stock&utm_medium=banner&utm_campaign=back_in_stock"
            target="_blank"
          >
            <span>Powered by</span>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 106 106" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M106 82C106 68.7452 95.2548 58 82 58C68.7452 58 58 68.7452 58 82C58 95.2548 68.7452 106 82 106C95.2548 106 106 95.2548 106 82Z" fill="currentColor"/>
              <path d="M0 82C0 95.25 10.75 106 24 106C37.25 106 48 95.25 48 82V58H24C10.75 58 0 68.75 0 82ZM16 86C13.79 86 12 84.21 12 82C12 79.79 13.79 78 16 78C18.21 78 20 79.79 20 82C20 84.21 18.21 86 16 86ZM32 86C29.79 86 28 84.21 28 82C28 79.79 29.79 78 32 78C34.21 78 36 79.79 36 82C36 84.21 34.21 86 32 86Z" fill="currentColor"/>
              <path d="M0 24C0 37.25 10.75 48 24 48H48V24C48 10.75 37.25 0 24 0C10.75 0 0 10.75 0 24ZM16 28C13.79 28 12 26.21 12 24C12 21.79 13.79 20 16 20C18.21 20 20 21.79 20 24C20 26.21 18.21 28 16 28ZM32 28C29.79 28 28 26.21 28 24C28 21.79 29.79 20 32 20C34.21 20 36 21.79 36 24C36 26.21 34.21 28 32 28Z" fill="currentColor"/>
